{"type": "article", "id": 4955, "title": "Missoni 旅行套装", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-06T07:58:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233511t5LBkqEpITN0GeHh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t意大利针织品牌米索尼（Missoni）日前为四季酒店专门设计推出了一款旅行套装，极具休闲的意大利风情，内含一条毛毯与一个枕头，可以随身携带前往旅行目的地。设计师用皮革背带将毛毯与枕头卷在一起进行收纳，为用户节省了空间。提供了两种男女皆宜的配色，定价 605－632 美元（约合人民币 3775－3944 元）不等，可在位于霍阿拉拉、茂宜岛、奥兰多以及拉奈岛的四季酒店购得。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335096jN3OAsBikUfLZQ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233510nKxwoRIzgJH8QDXv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233510IgPn1VvYMSwFdqT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}